Module com.bcs2024.knapsack
Package com.bcs2024.knapsack.util

Class ShapesAndRotations

java.lang.Object
com.bcs2024.knapsack.util.ShapesAndRotations
public class ShapesAndRotations extends Object
ShapesAndRotations manages the predefined shapes and rotations of parcels used in the knapsack problem. It provides methods to access these shapes and their rotations, based on parcel type.

    • getShape

      public int[][][] getShape(String parcelType, int rotation)
      Retrieves a specific shape and rotation for a given parcel type.
      Parameters:
      parcelType - The type of the parcel (e.g., "A", "B", "C", "L", "P", "T").
      rotation - The rotation index of the shape.
      Returns:
      The 3D array representing the shape of the parcel in the specified rotation.
